product.name: Pet Flap Door 2 Ways Locking Dog Wall Entry Pet Door with Transparent Flap for Dogs (Medium)
product.description:
Find pruducts that will please your cat and dog at PetPrime!
Give your Pet the Freedom to Come and Go
The Pet Prime Plastic Pet Door gives your pet the freedom to go in and out on their own time. Let your pet choose when it's bathroom time or time to play, so you and your pet can live happy together.
To find the right place for the pet door,mark your pet's shoulder height on the door, then use the provided template to trace the outline of the door.
Cut along the traced template line.
Drill 1 hole on each corner of the square.
Place the pet door frame into the door and secure the frame with screws so your pet can have the freedom to go outside on his own time!
Dog Door

product.bullet_points:
• ULTIMATE CONVENIENCE: Super convenience for owners, the pet door offers your pets the freedom and independence to come and go as they pleased
• 2 WAY MODELS, SIMPLE OPERATION: The 2 Way adaptable locking system pet door provides owners control over their pet's movements, ensuring safety and peace of mind. Easy to operate : open in/out; closed: only inside/only outside
• EASY INSTALLATION: Our 2 Way Pet Door can be Easily installed with the provided cutting template and installation guide. Fitting the Pet Door into thicker Doors has been made simple with the optional tunnel extension
• DURABLE MATERIALS: Made of weather-resistant plastic to ensure the comfortable and. Flexible transparent door flap allows for your pet's comfort and ease of use. The sturdy heavy duty metal bar at lower end of flap keeps the door in place when it's free
• AVAILABLE IN 3 SIZES: The Pet Flap Door includes three sizes with Small, Medium and Large (sold separately). Your satisfaction is our priority. Please let us know with any question - we are here to help
